
		 COMMANDS
preciona mayuscula Z dos veces, el cual hara la misma funcion que :x

al precionar ctrl z se suspende la  sesion, se sale de vim y volever a entrar no esta tu contenido: peros solo se supendio
para recuperarlo o volover a la sesion preciona en la terminal del sistema "fg"
ctrl g muestra la nombre del fichero en que estamos trabajando

			VISUAL MODALITY
*instead on entering	"vim file" enter "vienw file"
*in this mode it doesn't let us save but we can force   :w!

			CURSOR MOVEMENT
H,J,K,L.   h=left, l=right, j=down and h=up ........... n=1,2,3,4,5,6,..N
to go to the end: G
go to the beginnig of the word (right)--> w      and left--> b
						N times--> 5  w        and n=1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8...N
go to the end of the word: e
						N times--> 7 e      and n=1,2,3,4,3,...N
to go the end of the line---> $
						N---->5 $    and n=1.2.3..N
to go the beginning of the line--> 0
						does not have for 0

			CURSOR MOVEMENT TWO
search by charater on a line (right)--> f and character to search, example "b" other example " " space character, and left--> F
						N----> 7 f character to search, example "a"
search    character-1 position (right)---> t charater     and left---> T character
			
			CURSOR MOVEMENT THRE
set number, set number!
to move to a specific line----> n G   where n=1,2,3,4,5,6...n, example-->10 G. 	
					other form mode command-->  :n      example-->   :10
scroll---> crtl e=down   and ctrl y=up
	taster way-->crtl d=down  and crtl u=up
	move through each empty line--> up={    and down=}   incrementally---> n{   and  n}  n=1,2,3,4...
	
	
